title: Sawbones: The Glass Delusion
description:
This week, Dr. Sydnee and Justin delve into the strange story of the king who thought he was made of glass, and the many he might have convinced that they were too.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
